jasima.core.util

类 ResultSaver

  • java.lang.Object
    • jasima.core.util.AbstractResultSaver
      • jasima.core.util.ResultSaver
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    ExperimentListener, NotifierListener<Experiment,Experiment.ExperimentMessage>
    直接已知子类:
    ExcelSaver

    public class ResultSaver
extends AbstractResultSaver
    This class uses Java's serialization mechanism to save experiment results in a binary file.

    This file can later is later converted to a final output format, so usually a subclass of ResultSaver is used, e.g., ExcelSaver.

    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt
